OL,3,CFamily's plea after tributes to former
OL,4,Clollipop man stolen outside school
OL,6,FThe family of a lollipop man loved by
OL,7,Fgenerations of children in his
OL,8,Fcommunity say they are "devastated"
OL,9,Fthat tributes left near the school
OL,10,Fwhere he worked following his death
OL,11,Fhave been stolen.
OL,13,FDave York, known as "Dave The Lollipop
OL,14,FMan' in Wallasey, Wirral, died aged 76
OL,15,Fon 14 July.
OL,17,FFlowers and tributes were left outside
OL,18,FMount Primary School in New Brighton
OL,19,Ffollowing his death, but two people
OL,20,Fwere later caught on camera removing
OL,21,Fsome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
