PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784656151
OL,3,CFamily's plea after tributes to former
OL,4,Clollipop man stolen outside school
OL,6,FPosting on social media about the
OL,7,Fincident, his daughter-in-law Kerry
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's incredibly upsetting and
OL,9,Fdifficult to understand why anyone
OL,10,Fwould do something so heartless.
OL,12,F"They even returned a second time and
OL,13,Ftook the lot."
OL,15,FShe added: "We're not looking for
OL,16,Fconfrontation - we'd simply like to
OL,17,Fknow who these people are and,
OL,18,Fhopefully, understand why this
OL,19,Fhappened."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
