CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784656151
OL,3,CFamily's plea after tributes to former
OL,4,Clollipop man stolen outside school
OL,6,FPaying tribute to Dave, Friends of
OL,7,FMount Primary School - an online
OL,8,Fcommunity page - said they will miss
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F"Dave was the person that not only
OL,12,Fcrossed us all over safely, but that
OL,13,Fgave big smiles and waves, high 5s and
OL,14,Ffriendly words on our walks to and
OL,15,Ffrom school, whatever the weather," it
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
